title: E-Commerce Website
description: This project is a full-stack e-commerce website with payment integration, product management, and admin dashboard. Users can browse products, add to cart, checkout, and make secure payments. Admin can manage products, orders, and customers with an intuitive dashboard.

title: Portfolio Website
description: A personal portfolio website with smooth animations, blog section, and contact form integration. Built using React.js and Tailwind CSS. Fully responsive and optimized for SEO.
